e a system of academic success programs and services that proactively facilitates the successful transition and academic performance of cadets throughout their time at VMI  Simultaneously we will enhance the reputation and credibility of the MAC by educating stakeholders about the capabilities and possibilities of the MAC so that programs and services are fully utilized and valued  Latest News from the MAC  Group Study Sessions  GSS have started for the spring semester  GSS are led by one or two upperclass cadets who earned a B or better in the course at VMI  GSS  are Group Study Sessions that have a faculty member working closely with the cadet leaders to help them plan the sessions and debrief assess following each week s group meeting  The faculty for GSS  also attend the weekly group meeting to observe  mentor  and assist where needed  Please check out the most up to date schedule on the Group Study Sessions page For more information on Group Study Sessions  contact MAJ Coates  coatestk vmi edu   Position Openings  We are looking for GSS facilitators for the courses listed below  If you are interested  please email MAJ Coates at coatestk vmi edu  CH 224  PE 380  AR 102   202  SP 102   202  Individual Meetings Available MAC staff is available from 0800 1630  Monday   Friday for individuals meetings  Interested cadets can either schedule an appointment or drop by  Possible topics can include setting goals  planning your time so you can do everything you need to do and want to do  reading for comprehension and retention  note taking  and test preparation and test taking  Cadets with suggestions of programs and services that the MAC should consider offering are also encouraged to come by the office  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 